Whereas a total of 273 members of the Armed Services from
			 36 States across the United States were killed while serving in Beirut,
			 Lebanon, from 1982 to 1984;

Whereas remembering those who lost their lives and those
			 who served in Beirut would enhance public awareness of the roots of the war on
			 terror and strengthen public resolve to rid the world of evil;
